T1  - Welfare Implications of Inventory-Driven Dynamic Pricing
AU  - Stamatopoulos, Ioannis
AU  - Chehrazi, Naveed
AU  - Bassamboo, Achal
Y1  - 2019/10/24
PY  - 2019
DA  - 2019/12/01
